n去交易紀錄睇［平倉］欄會寫住［完成］<br />\n利申一通新手"},{"pid":"533fed8043d0671c734dbfe663361e00977138ac","tid":105433,"uid":26406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T01:40:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>唔算<br />\n<br />\n你依加理論上冇倉 但其實你有2張係手<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你下邊沽個張係 時段沽出<br />\n<br />\n你平倉要 「時段買入」</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁而加我要點做？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你張圖個度最右邊 <br />\n<br />\n買左個張 依加沽<br />\n沽左個張 依加買<br />\n<br />\n利申：記得係咁 錯左唔好怪我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e76d6944a40417b3e38b7e2c08009bcad3f72a94","tid":105433,"uid":37760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T01:45:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"84c5ae43d92838c950d884f830469979c5ba5df9","tid":105433,"uid":49260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T02:00:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/03/095907_77532004d6cd39e3556df8f9e727cca6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F03%2F095907_77532004d6cd39e3556df8f9e727cca6.jpg&h=c9a743ce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n比佢玩撚死<br />\n終於平撚倒"},{"pid":"3c4a78ba7db4fe2dd2567236f1e98f0e523d3fe4","tid":105433,"uid":49260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T02:06:39.000Z","msg":"Thx 各位巴打"},{"pid":"964ced877e8eaa2cd95b3bbe79b760e556b8372b","tid":105433,"uid":9136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T02:13:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/03/095907_77532004d6cd39e3556df8f9e727cca6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F03%2F095907_77532004d6cd39e3556df8f9e727cca6.jpg&h=c9a743ce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n比佢玩撚死<br />\n終於平撚倒</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 笑撚死"},{"pid":"d318ca8d43b7a43f11184c55f120c085fdda606d","tid":105433,"uid":26406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T02:17:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/03/095907_77532004d6cd39e3556df8f9e727cca6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F03%2F095907_77532004d6cd39e3556df8f9e727cca6.jpg&h=c9a743ce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n比佢玩撚死<br />\n終於平撚倒</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 笑撚死</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一通係咁<br />\n<br />\n好耐之前我都試過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afd55553aadb612acb6419c3f8d6dca1fa4aa415","tid":105433,"uid":32525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T02:35:47.000Z","msg":"點解其他券商唔會咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6936d4bf5cb297cf540f0b9dcc8fcfe0811c6a76","tid":105433,"uid":24015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T02:38:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解其他券商唔會咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其他唔會有日倉呢回事<br />\n你唔記得平就自動過夜"},{"pid":"a271b81487b960aa52d796a781d778a66893401f","tid":105433,"uid":49260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T10:27:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>點解其他券商唔會咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其他唔會有日倉呢回事<br />\n你唔記得平就自動過夜</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n樣野勁on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"669d3579426377081ab7e315ceb555c3421fb57b","tid":105433,"uid":8246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T12:21:02.000Z","msg":"其實好簡單，禁搬倉就得，你呢個情況叫做鎖倉，你就算唔理佢，佢過市果陣都會自動平，呢個情況會hold住按金<br />\n<br />\n因為你開左唔同時段既倉，下次想平倉，用翻相同時段就自動平<br />\n<br />\n第一次用都比佢玩左次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c0495505af88634fe8aff0ba7a11edf8093ea66","tid":105433,"uid":49260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T12:32:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實好簡單，禁搬倉就得，你呢個情況叫做鎖倉，你就算唔理佢，佢過市果陣都會自動平，呢個情況會hold住按金<br />\n<br />\n因為你開左唔同時段既倉，下次想平倉，用翻相同時段就自動平<br />\n<br />\n第一次用都比佢玩左次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n禁完搬倉會點？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2166185ca7b9e9edb97739e3bec01d8f0fa6dc43","tid":105433,"uid":29008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T07:09:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/03/095907_77532004d6cd39e3556df8f9e727cca6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F03%2F095907_77532004d6cd39e3556df8f9e727cca6.jpg&h=c9a743ce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n比佢玩撚死<br />\n終於平撚倒</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 笑撚死</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一通係咁<br />\n<br />\n好耐之前我都試過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n笑到抽筋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}